partition p4 values less than (2500),
partition p5 values less than (MAXVALUE));
alter table t_tinyuint drop partition (p5,p3);
alter table t_tinyuint add partition (partition p5 values less than (MAXVALUE));
alter table t_tinyuint reorganize partition p4 into (partition p3 values less than (256),partition p4 values less than (2500));
